    <h3>Theme Sample.</h3>
    <hr />
    <h4>1. Setting a theme for the whole app</h4>
    <p>You can set a default theme for your app via configuration of the app.</p>
    <p>Example 'config.yaml' would look like this:</p>
    <pre>
        ...
        <b>theme : org.wso2.carbon.uuf.sample.theme.default</b>
        ...
    </pre>
    <h4>2. Setting a theme for a session</h4>
    <p>You can set a different theme for each session at runtime. Session-scope theme has a higher precedence than app-scope theme.</p>
    <p>See the sample <a href="{{@contextPath}}/theme/session-scope"><b>HERE</b></a>.</p>
{{/fillZone}}